1) /etc/postfix/main.cf:
------------------------
relay_domains = hash:/srv/thialfi/postfix/domain
transport_maps = hash:/srv/thialfi/postfix/transport

2) /etc/postfix/master.cf:
--------------------------
thialfi   unix  -       n       n       -       -       pipe
  flags=FRhu  user=nobody argv=/srv/thialfi/scripts/receive-mail ${sender} ${recipient}

3) In /srv/thialfi/postfix/
---------------------------
- Update 'domain' and 'transport' files
- Run 'make'
